ktige forvaltningsansvaret rovviltnemndene har f\u00e5tt og for de f\u00f8ringene Stortinget har gitt i rovviltforliket. Det har de etter min mening ikke gjort i denne saken, sier Brekk."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag|oppdal"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "edcd8aff0b293bdd44f80d9b1891ae069710c39d210b8b0a727383674ead1a6e"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-08-11T19:26:37.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "\u2013 Mattilsynet tok litt for mye M\u00f8llers tran da de varslet beitenekt."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article2132415.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Adressa%20Rovdyr%20169_JUST"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/f2814bfeb17e167bf918a3dbac31dcb234f51f14.jpg?5908bece"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Mattilsynet tok for mye M\u00f8llers tran -adressa.no", "Strammer opp Mattilsynet", "Sp vs SV"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "f2814bfeb17e167bf918a3dbac31dcb234f51f14"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "oppdal", "sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "health-and-fitness"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["departementet legger", "varsle beitenekt", "prioriterte beiteomr\u00e5der", "vedtak", "beitenekt", "fatte vedtak"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["h\u00f8yesteretts", "rendalsdommen", "mattilsynet", "m\u00f8llers", "anne marit og hans sn\u00f8ve", "stortinget", "milj\u00f8verndepartementets", "milj\u00f8departementet", "hans sn\u00f8ve"]}, {"field"